    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Mendel's Garden?</h2>Mendel's garden is a gardening game where every plant has one or more traits, many of which are hidden. You harvest seeds from these plants and try to isolate these hidden traits by planting and growing the seeds. Craft items by combining seeds with different traits and use these items to progress further in the world.<br><br><strong>Harvest seeds from plants with hidden traits.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132160/extras/28d9c1acd8aa11e59b8e8b358d22a326.poster.avif?t=1643476563\" width=626 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132160/extras/28d9c1acd8aa11e59b8e8b358d22a326.webm?t=1643476563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132160/extras/28d9c1acd8aa11e59b8e8b358d22a326.mp4?t=1643476563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Grow the seeds to isolate these traits.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132160/extras/a1d576aa800453cee346edb15c52b21c.poster.avif?t=1643476563\" width=626 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132160/extras/a1d576aa800453cee346edb15c52b21c.webm?t=1643476563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132160/extras/a1d576aa800453cee346edb15c52b21c.mp4?t=1643476563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Craft items by mixing different traits and use them to move further in the world.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132160/extras/e98f9788ded40b4f9e414b58bcf5542f.poster.avif?t=1643476563\" width=626 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132160/extras/e98f9788ded40b4f9e414b58bcf5542f.webm?t=1643476563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132160/extras/e98f9788ded40b4f9e414b58bcf5542f.mp4?t=1643476563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The gardens </h2>The world contains multiple gardens<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1. Grow plants instantly using a special kind of rain.<br></li><li>2. Overcome barriers by crafting the appropriate plants or items and explore the deepest parts of the gardens.<br></li><li>3. Discover the story behind the garden as you progress.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>Set in the Bhumi universe Mendel's garden explores the story of <strong>Mendel</strong> and his journey. Mendel ventures into unknown lands teeming with helpful and harmful plants to learn about them and understand them. In doing so he stumbles upon ancient secrets, dark mysteries and most importantly finds his purpose in this strange world.<br><br>Trailer Music credits<br>Clear water by Kevin MacLeod <br>Licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 3.0 License",
